{"parentUuid":"2254863a-8379-458e-b699-1b56f6c2ade9","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Rd3pKRD3YiEwqVFD8rpRGp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Honestly, it depends on what your review catches:\n\n**Simplify → review**\n- Pro: reviewer isn't distracted by dead code, dupes, or obvious cleanups you'd have caught yourself — feedback focuses on substance\n- Pro: you self-correct cheaply before another set of eyes is spent\n- Con: if review reshapes the approach, polish was wasted\n- Con: simplify can delete scaffolding (logs, intermediate vars) that would've helped the reviewer follow your reasoning\n\n**Review → simplify**\n- Pro: one polish pass at the end covers both your code and anything review introduced\n- Pro: no wasted effort when review changes direction\n- Con: reviewer wades through noise and may flag things you'd have removed anyway, inflating the diff\n- Con: easy to skip the simplify pass once review is \"done\" and ship cruft\n\nRule of thumb: if your reviews are mostly nits/style, simplify first. If reviews tend to challenge the approach, review first."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":182,"cache_read_input_tokens":23897,"output_tokens":549,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":182,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":549,"cache_read_input_tokens":23897,"cache_creation_input_tokens":182,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":182},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011Ca1JGmKBGVTFpYQ98q3pm","type":"assistant","uuid":"172dbde0-ca1f-43de-b31d-1c3e04f60869","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:29:47.343Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/robertlopez/repos/harness","ses